{
  "chapter": "075",
  "title": "孟尝君列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "田婴封薛",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">靖郭君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐宣王</span>的庶<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威王（齐威王）</span>时起任职当权，和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邹忌\">成侯（邹忌）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹忌</span>及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>率兵救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邹忌\">成侯（邹忌）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>争宠，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邹忌\">成侯（邹忌）</span>陷害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>惧，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的边邑，不胜，逃亡。恰遇<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威王（齐威王）</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣王（齐宣王）</span>即位，知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邹忌\">成侯（邹忌）</span>陷害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>，便再召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣王（齐宣王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>一起<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马陵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>之，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏太子申\">申（魏太子申）</span>并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣王（齐宣王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>归服于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏惠王</span>会<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐宣王</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东阿</span>之南，结盟而去。第二年，又与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁惠王</span>会于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甄</span>。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁惠王</span>去世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣王（齐宣王）</span>九年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐宣王</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏襄王</span>会于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐州</span>，互相称王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚威王</span>听说，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>发怒。第二年，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐州</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>师，派人驱逐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张丑</span>游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚威王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威王（齐威王）</span>才停止。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>十一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣王（齐宣王）</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>即位。即位三年，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "五月子生",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀人</span>。他的贱妾生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五日（时长）</span>出生。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>告诉他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲说：\"不要抚养。\" 他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲偷偷抚养长大。长大后，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲通过兄弟把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>引见给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>对他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲发怒说：\"我叫你扔掉这个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，你竟敢把他养大，为什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>叩首，接着说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>为什么不抚养<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五月</span>生的孩子？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>说：\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五月</span>生的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，长到与门框齐高，将不利其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>说：\"人生受命于天呢？还是受命于门户？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>沉默。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>说：\"如果受命于天，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>有什么可忧虑。如果受命于门户，可以把门加高，谁还能长到那里！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>不要说了。\""
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "孟尝君主家",
      "text": "过了许久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>找机会问他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>叫什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>说：\"叫<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子。\" \"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>叫什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>说：\"叫玄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>。\" \"玄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>叫什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>说：\"不知道了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>当权做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>相，至今已经<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三王</span>了，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国没有扩大而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>私家财富积累至<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万金</span>，门下不见一个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤者</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>听说将门必出<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>，相门必出<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>后宫穿着绫罗绸缎而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>得不到粗布短衣，仆妾有剩余的粱肉而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>吃不饱糟糠。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>还要增加积蓄，想留给不知是谁的后人，却忘了公家之事日渐损耗，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>私下感到奇怪。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>便礼待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>，让他主家事接待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>日渐增多，名声闻于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都派人请<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>公<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴</span>立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>答应了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田婴\">婴（田婴）</span>去世后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">靖郭君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>果然继位于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "招贤待客",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，招致<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>宾客及有罪之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亡人</span>，都归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>舍弃家产厚待他们，因此倾动天下之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>，无论贵贱都与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>同等待遇。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>接待客人谈话，屏风后常有侍史，负责记录<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>与客人谈话的内容，询问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>的居处。客人离去后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>已派使者慰问，赠送礼物给他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>曾一次夜间招待客人用餐，有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>遮住灯光。客人发怒，以为饭菜不平等，辍食告辞。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>起身，亲自拿自己的饭与他比较。客人惭愧，自刎而死。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人因此多归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>对客人无所挑选，都善待之。人人都自以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>与自己亲近。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "苏代劝止入秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>听说他贤能，先派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">泾阳君</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>为质，请求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>将入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>都不愿他去，谏阻，他不听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>对他说：\"今天早上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：苏代\">代（苏代）</span>从外面来，看见木偶人和土偶人相互交谈。木偶人说：'天下雨，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>就要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>坏了。'土偶人说：'我生于土，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>就归于土。如今天下雨，把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>冲走，不知要停在哪里。'如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>是虎狼之国，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>要去，若不得归，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>岂不要被土偶人所笑吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>便作罢。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "鸡鸣狗盗",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十五年（时长）</span>，终究还是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>即以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。有人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>贤能，又是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的宗族，如今相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，必先为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>而后为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>就危险了。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>便作罢。将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>禁，准备<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>派人求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>的幸姬求救。幸姬说：\"妾愿得<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">狐白裘</span>。\" 这时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>有一件<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">狐白裘</span>，价值<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>，天下无双，入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>已献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>，再没有别的裘。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>为此发愁，遍问客人，无人能答。最下座的有个能做狗偷的，说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>能得到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">狐白裘</span>。\" 便夜里装狗进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>宫藏室中，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>出已献的狐白裘，献给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸姬</span>。幸姬替他向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>求情，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>释放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>得以出来，立即驰去，换了过关凭证，改名换姓以出关。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时辰\">夜半（时辰）</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">函谷关</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>后悔放走<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>，派人去找已离开，立即派人驰马追他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>到关，关法<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时辰\">鸡鸣（时辰）</span>才能放客出关，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>担心追兵赶到，客中下座有能学鸡鸣的，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸡</span>跟着齐鸣，于是发关文出关。出关大约一顿饭的工夫，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵追到关，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>已出关，便回去了。起初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>把这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>列入宾客，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>都以为羞耻，待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国之难时，终是这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>救了他。从此以后，客人都心服口服。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "过赵击人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>经过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">平原君（赵胜）</span>以宾客之礼接待他。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>贤能，出来看他，都笑道：\"原以为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>公魁梧高大，现在看来，不过是矮小男子而已。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>听了，大怒。随行的客人跳下车，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">斫</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百人</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>一县而去。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "复相于齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>自觉不安，因为是他派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>去的。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>到了，便任他为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>相，掌管政事。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "苏代劝合秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>怨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，想以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，再与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，并向西<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>借兵借粮。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>为西<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>对他说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>已<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">叶</span>以北之地以使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>强大，如今又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>来增益它们。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>南无<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>患，西无<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>患，则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>就危险了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>必轻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>而畏<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>担心。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不如让敝国深入和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，也不借兵借粮。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>临<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">函谷</span>而不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，让敝国以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的意图对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>说'<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>公必不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>以使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>强大。他<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，是想王让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王割<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东国</span>给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，并让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>以讲和'。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>让敝国以此施惠于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>得以不被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>而以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东国</span>自救，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>必愿意。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王得出，必感激<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>得<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东国</span>而更强，而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>世代无忧。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>不大弱，处于三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>之西，三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>必重视<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。\" <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>公说：\"好。\" 于是让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>祝贺<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，使三国不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，而不向西<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>借兵借粮。这时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>扣留他，所以想一定要使他放出。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>终究没放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "魏子自刭",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏子</span>替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>收封邑的租税，三次往返都没有缴收一次。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>问他，他回答说：\"有一位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤者</span>，私下借给他了，所以没有征收。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>生气地辞退了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏子</span>。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，有人在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>面前诋毁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>将作乱。\" 等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田甲</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">劫</span>持<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>怀疑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>便出奔。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏子</span>所借给的那位贤者听说此事，就上书说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>不作乱，请以身作保，便自刎于宫门以证明<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>的清白。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>大惊，便追查验证，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>果然无反谋，便再次召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>便以病为由谢绝，告老回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>答应了。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "苏代谋驱吕礼",
      "text": "此后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>逃亡之将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，想困住<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：苏代\">代（苏代）</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周最</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>最忠厚，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王却驱逐他，听信<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亲弗</span>而任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>为相，是想拉拢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>联合，则<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亲弗</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>就受重视了。他们受重用，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>必轻视<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不如立即北进，趋向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>以和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，收用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周最</span>以表厚道，并反转<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王的诚信，又禁止天下之变。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>没有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，天下就归心<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亲弗</span>必逃走，那么<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王跟谁治理国家呢！\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>听从他的计策，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>嫉害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "致书穰侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>害怕，便送信给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏厓</span>说：\"我听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>想以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>招揽<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>是天下强国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>必将被轻视。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>联合以威逼三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>必将兼相两国，这是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的关系重视<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>。若<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>免于天下兵灾，他对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的仇恨必定深重。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>不如劝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>，我请以所得之地<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>畏<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>之强，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>必重<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>以拉拢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋国</span>被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>耗敝而畏<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>必重<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>以拉拢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。这样<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>为功，挟<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>为重；这是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>而得<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>邑，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>都重视<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。若<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>再被任用，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>必大困窘。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰侯</span>向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>劝说<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>逃亡。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "薛绝嗣",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，更加骄纵，想除去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>惧，便到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏昭王\">昭王（魏昭王）</span>任他为相，西联<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>逃亡在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>，便死在那里。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐襄王\">襄王（齐襄王）</span>立，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>中立于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间，不归属任何一方。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐襄王\">襄王（齐襄王）</span>新立，畏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>，与他联和，再次亲善<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>公。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>死后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸子</span>争立，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">孟尝（孟尝君）</span>绝嗣而无后。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "冯驩弹铗",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">客</span>，穿着草鞋来见他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>说：\"先生远道屈尊，有何指教<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，我以贫身来归<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>把他安置在传舍<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十日（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">传舍长</span>：\"客人在干什么？\" 回答说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯驩\">冯（冯驩）</span>先生很穷，只有一把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>，且用草绳缠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">柄</span>。弹他的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>而歌：'长<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铗</span>啊回去吧，吃饭没有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>。'\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>把他迁到幸舍，有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>吃了。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五日（时长）</span>，又问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">传舍长</span>。回答说：\"客人又弹<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>而歌：'长<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铗</span>啊回去吧，出门没有车。'\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>把他迁到<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">代舍</span>，出入有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乘舆</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>了。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五日（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>又问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">传舍长</span>。舍长回答说：\"先生又曾弹<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>而歌：'长<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铗</span>啊回去吧，没有办法养家。'\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>不悦。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "焚券",
      "text": "过了一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>没有说什么。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>当时相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，封邑在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>。他有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千人</span>。邑的税收不够供养宾客，于是派人到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>放贷。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">岁馀（时长）</span>钱未收回，借钱的人多数不能交利息，客食将无以为继。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>忧虑，问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">左右</span>：\"谁可派往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>去收债？\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">传舍长</span>说：\"<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">代舍</span>客人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯驩\">冯公（冯驩）</span>形貌辩才甚好，是长者，没有别的本事，可以派他去收债。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>便请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>来说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>不知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>不肖，幸而光临<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>者有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千馀人</span>，邑的收入不够供养<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>，所以到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>放贷取息。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>今年歉收，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>多不能付利息。如今客食恐不给，请先生去催收。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"好。\" 告辞而行，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，召集<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>钱的人前来，收得息钱<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万</span>。便多酿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>，买肥<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>，召集所有借钱者，能付息的都来，不能付息的也都来，都带着借债的券书前来核对。整齐地摆开酒席，当日<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>置<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>。酒酣之际，拿着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">券</span>如前核对，能付息的，约定还期；贫穷不能付息的，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">券</span>烧掉。说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>之所以借钱，是为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>没有本钱做本业；之所以求息，是为了养客。如今富足的约期还债，贫穷的焚券以免除。诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>尽情饮食吧。有这样的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，怎能辜负呢！\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">坐者</span>都起身，再拜。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "孟尝君释然",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>烧了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">券书</span>，怒而派人召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯驩\">驩（冯驩）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯驩\">驩（冯驩）</span>到了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千人</span>，所以在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>放贷。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>的奉邑少，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>还多有不按时交息的，客食恐不足，所以请先生去收。听说先生得钱后，就大置<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">牛酒</span>而烧<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">券书</span>，为什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"是的。不多备<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">牛酒</span>就不能召齐所有借债人，无从得知他们有余不足。有余的，约定还期。不足的，即使守着催十年也无济于事，利息越多，催得急，就逃亡不见自行豁免了。若催得急，终无以偿还，上则使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>有好利不爱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>之名，下则有背离上意抵赖负债之名，这不是激励<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>彰显<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>声誉的方法。焚毁无用的虚假债券，舍弃不可得的虚假账目，让<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>亲近<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>而彰显<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的美名，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>还有什么疑惑呢！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>便拍手致谢。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "冯驩说秦齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的谗毁所惑，认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>名声超过君主而专擅<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐国</span>之权，便废黜<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。 诸客见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>被废，都离去了。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"借<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>一辆，能入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>者，必能让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>在国中受重视而封邑增广，可以吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>便整备<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">币</span>派他去。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>西去游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王说：\"天下游<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>倚车西入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的，无不想使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>强而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>弱；倚车东入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的，无不想使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>强而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>弱。这是雄雌之国，势不两立为雄，雄者得天下。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王跪起身问他：\"如何使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>不为雌？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"王也知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>废黜<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>吗？\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王说：\"听说了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>受重于天下的，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王因谗毁废黜他，他心里怨恨，必背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>；背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐国</span>的实情、人事的真情，尽归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>所有，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地可得，岂止为雄而已！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>急派人载<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">币</span>暗中迎<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>，不可失时。如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>觉悟，再用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>，则雌雄归属难料了。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王大悦，便派<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>十乘、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span>百镒去迎<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>告辞先行，到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，劝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王说：\"天下游<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>倚车东入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>者，无不想使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>强而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>弱；倚车西入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>者，无不想使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>强而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>弱。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>齐雌雄<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">之国</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>强则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>弱，势不两雄。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私闻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>十乘载<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span>百镒来迎<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>不西去便罢，西去相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>则天下归之，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>为雄而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>为雌，雌则<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临淄</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span>危矣。王何不抢在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>使之前，恢复<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>，再增封邑以谢罪？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>必喜而受。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>虽强国，岂能用请人作相而迎人之事！这就挫败了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的谋划，断了它称霸的策略。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王说：\"好。\" 便派人到边境等候<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>使。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>使的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>刚入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>境，使者就驰回告之，王召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>恢复他的相位，并还给他原来的封邑，又增<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千户</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>复相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，调<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>而去了。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "感叹宾客",
      "text": "自从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王毁废<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸客</span>都离去了。后来召他复位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>迎接。还未到，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>叹息说：\"文一向好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">客</span>，接待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">客</span>不敢有所怠慢，有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span>三千多人，先生都知道。客人看<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一日（时长）</span>被废，都背<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>而去，没有人回头看<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>。如今赖先生使我复位，这些客人还有什么面目再见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>？再来见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孟尝君\">文（孟尝君）</span>的，必唾他的脸大辱他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>挽着缰绳下拜。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>迎接他，说：\"先生为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">客</span>们道歉吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"不是为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">客</span>道歉，是因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的话说错了。事物有必然之至，事理有固然之势，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>知道吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>说：\"愚笨，不懂您的意思。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯驩</span>说：\"生者必有死，这是事物必然之至；富贵则<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">多士</span>，贫贱则寡友，这是事理固然之势。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>难道没见过赶集的人吗？清早，侧身挤进市门；<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时辰\">日暮（时辰）</span>之后，经过市场的人甩着膀子头也不回。不是爱清早恶日暮，是所期望的物品早已不在市中。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>失位，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>都离去，不必怨恨<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人并断绝<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>之路。希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>仍像从前那样对待客人。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>再拜说：\"敬从教诲。听了先生的话，岂敢不照办。\""
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我曾经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，那里的风俗闾里多凶暴不驯的子弟，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>不同。问其缘故，有人说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>招致天下任侠之士，奸人入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六万馀家</span>。\" 世间传闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>好客自喜，其名不虚传。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "靖郭之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威王（齐威王）</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>。 既强其国，实高其门。 好客喜<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，见重于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：平原君\">平原（平原君）</span>。 〘※鸡鸣狗盗〙，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯驩\">冯暖（冯驩）</span>。 如何转眼之间，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>县徒存！"
    }
  }
}